Name: Coldiron Tribulation (I)
Desc: Apply Memory Imprint to all enemies at the beginning of each Cycle. For each other debuff currently on the enemy, apply 1 extra stack of Memory Imprint to that enemy. Each stack reduces the target's DMG dealt by <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]%</unbreak></color> for a maximum of <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#2[i]</unbreak></color> stacks. This effect lasts until the start of the next Cycle.

Challenge.Name: Win with at least <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> Cycle(s) left
Win with at least <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> Cycle(s) left
Have no downed characters
